| **Real-Time Data** | ✅ WebSocket | ⚠️ Polling | ⚠️ Delayed |
| **Multi-Wallet** | ✅ 4+ Wallets | ⚠️ Limited | ⚠️ Basic |
| **Advanced Trading** | ✅ Jupiter DEX | ✅ Native | ❌ None |
| **Risk Management** | ✅ AI-Powered | ❌ None | ⚠️ Basic |
| **User Experience** | ✅ Modern UI | ⚠️ Functional | ⚠️ Outdated |

### Market Positioning
- **Target Market**: Sophisticated DeFi users seeking professional tools
- **Pricing Strategy**: Freemium model with premium AI features
